&lt;p&gt;To cope with that complexity I think some kind of meta representation of those attributes is needed (even outside of the application) in xml or even excel file, so that on each change all mentioned code could be auto-generated (sql/orm queries, application code, templates). So it can help with development, but still testing and extra deployment is needed.&lt;/p&gt;

