&lt;p&gt;There has been a lot of talk recently about NoSQL.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The #1 reason why I hear people use NoSQL is because they start to de-normalize their DBMS data so much so, to increase performance, that they end up with just one table with all of their data within that single table.&lt;/p&gt;

